T1  - Developing Theory Through Simulation Methods
AU  - Davis, Jason P.
AU  - Eisenhardt, Kathleen M.
AU  - Bingham, Christopher B.
Y1  - 2007/04/01
PY  - 2007
DA  - 2007/04/01
